Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上是十八小时前\N传送过来的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这之后\N监视卫星就被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道是用什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是伟人吗？是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还在询问当中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:00:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过也没有特定的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被抢走的书\N已经在印度的市场发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Paper　Miss Deep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请妳们和贩卖商人贾亨接触
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,调查伟人的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和伟人本人接触的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望儘可能将他活捉回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是　遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把“永恆的爱恋”\N书面分析结果送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是从纽约拿回来的\N李里安塔鲁的发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是史帝夫製造公司的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过在英国和美国都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要给妳一项功课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你能爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天和今天\N因为对你止不住的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而潸然泪下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用…我的生命…\N爱你生生世世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦　请你继续爱我到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是写在空白地方的辞句
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过是随便乱写的罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…可是我觉得\N我好像在哪裡有听过耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这本书怎么这么髒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为旧了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就连书籤也都弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亏它还那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎？妳觉得这张书籤很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎？嗯　我觉得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送给妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦　谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我要送给我的亲密好友的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而妳就是我最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧　我就拿来用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带着它会身体健康
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果夹在爱情小说裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恋情就会开花结果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不看那种小说咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与其看小说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒不如去谈恋爱比较实际
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳说的是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来　真正的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却不像小说那样进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进展不顺利的真正爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟很幸福却是假想的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要哪一种？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我问的问题实在太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是没有任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就可以去市集\N买印度披巾回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好　开始准备登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是来回答妳刚才的问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得…\N真正的爱情可能会很美好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然也有伤心　痛苦的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且不管是什么样的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己都可以当主角
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不要说那些无关紧要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在有任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集中精神工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好　去叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南西．幕张26岁　在日本出生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剑桥大学毕业后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,担任英国警察的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年后\N转任大英图书馆特殊工作部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有违反纪律\N以及不履行任务的纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然没有不对劲的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会不会想太多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纯白洁淨有时候\N反而比全黑还令人可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新调查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次要不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更深入　更广泛地去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，我是裘克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们到贾亨的店了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请妳们进去打听看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万事拜託了\N我相信妳们办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾亨先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像不在家耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们闯进去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像烧过什么东西\N屋子裡很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请妳们搜查店内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们进来打扰了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你如果不出声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会继续打扰下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务第一 The Paper
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾亨先生　请你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是伟人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫做玄奘\N西天玄奘三藏法师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄奘　好　进行搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是来拿这本书的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错\N我曾经为了取经来到这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过现在我要的只有那本书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们的伎俩\N对修得正果的我是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢去修道成仙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳先逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碍事的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是玄奘的搜索结果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我告诉妳敌人的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄奘是一位\N在七世纪时从中国到印度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取回佛经的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是“西游记”的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我四岁时就读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那本“西游记”是虚构的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过现在的他\N却有孙悟空的如意棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和猪八戒的喷火能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请妳暂时退回潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好　可是我担心南西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要担心我　还早得很咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要书！我一定要得到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是筋斗云
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该就快看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边
