Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！蒸气没了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请把影像放大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个也是蒸气…啊！
